<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6b6623f8-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s702a–6"><num value="702a–6">§ 702a–6.</num><heading> Drainage necessitated by floodway levees</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The United States shall provide the drainage made necessary by the construction of floodway levees included in the modified project.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id6b6623f9-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e">(<ref href="/us/act/1936-06-15/ch548/s6">June 15, 1936, ch. 548, § 6</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/49/1510">49 Stat. 1510</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
